@quangson91 
and you should detect when scrolled back to the end to re-enable `auto scroll to end`.
Does your fix include that?

@zoechi I updated this PR: https://github.com/flutter/flutter-intellij/pull/2488

now when user scroll update -> disable auto scroll to end.
when user scroll to the end (bottom) -> re-enable `auto scroll to end`.
